## 2. vManage

> Viptela OS platform. Basic System configuration alongside WAN and Management interfaces.

```text
config
 system
  host-name vManage
  system-ip 1.1.1.1
  site-id 100
  organization-name BKACAD-SDWAN
  vbond 10.0.0.10
 vpn 0
  interface eth1
   ip address 10.0.0.2/30
   tunnel-interface
    allow-service all
   no shutdown
  ip route 0.0.0.0/0 10.0.0.1
 vpn 512
  interface eth0
   ip address 192.168.1.211/24
   no shutdown
  ip route 0.0.0.0/0 192.168.1.1
 vpn 0
  no interface eth0
commit and-quit

```

