## 6. cEdge-HN (Site 101 – Hanoi)

> Cisco Catalyst 8000V – IOS-XE SD-WAN Mode.
> **Important:** Enable controller-mode before configuring using the command: `controller-mode enable`

### 6.1 Configure System + WAN biz-internet (Gi1)

```text
config-transaction
 hostname cEdge-HN
 system
  system-ip 1.1.1.101
  site-id 101
  organization-name BKACAD-SDWAN
  vbond 10.0.0.10
 exit
 interface GigabitEthernet1
  no shutdown
  ip address 10.0.1.2 255.255.255.252
 exit
 interface Tunnel1
  no shutdown
  ip unnumbered GigabitEthernet1
  tunnel source GigabitEthernet1
  tunnel mode sdwan
 exit
 sdwan
  interface GigabitEthernet1
   tunnel-interface
    encapsulation ipsec
    color biz-internet
    allow-service all
   exit
  exit
 ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.0.1.1
commit

```

### 6.2 Configure WAN mpls (Gi3)

```text
config-transaction
 interface GigabitEthernet3
  ip address 10.1.1.2 255.255.255.0
  no shutdown
 exit
 interface Tunnel3
  ip unnumbered GigabitEthernet3
  tunnel source GigabitEthernet3
  tunnel mode sdwan
  no shutdown
 exit
 sdwan
  interface GigabitEthernet3
   tunnel-interface
    encapsulation ipsec
    color mpls
    allow-service all
   exit
  exit
 ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.1.1.1
commit

```

### 6.3 Configure LAN VPN 10 (Gi2)

```text
config-transaction
 vrf definition 10
  rd 1:10
  address-family ipv4
  exit-address-family
 exit
 interface GigabitEthernet2
  no shutdown
  vrf forwarding 10
  ip address 10.10.1.1 255.255.255.0
 exit
 sdwan
  omp
   address-family ipv4 vrf 10
    advertise connected
    advertise static
   exit
  exit
 exit
commit

```

